<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-03-0041 </DOCNO><TEXT>This report describes a program to evaluate and upgrade internal dosimetrycapabilities at DOE and DOE contractor facilities. This is a multi-laboratory,long range effort that will upgrade internal dosimetry programs at DOEfacilities and will be interfaced closely with other DOE-sponsored programssuch as the various animal radiobiological studies, the plutonium anduranium registries, and other available research data. 2 refs.</TEXT></DOC>